title: Dive to Blue (October 2016)
synopsis: Famous Japanese creators challenge the possibilities of Marine-chan（the famous character of "Umimonogatari"） Co-Making brand new digital idol "iMarine-chan", original song and music video with Users. We put several meaning into "i" of iMarine, such as infinity, icon, internet, imagination, innovation, ideal and I.
related_anime: ['Sea Breeze', 'Deep Blue Song (September 2017)', 'Dive to Blue', 'Sunny Days!']
